图片来源：Press TV“ 伊朗新增1234例新冠肺炎病例，累计确诊4747例。
Source: Press TV: 1,234 new cases of crowns pneumonia have been diagnosed in Iran, with a cumulative total of 4,747.
另据法新社报道，伊朗新增17例死亡病例，累计124例。
According to AFP, Iran has 17 new cases of death, a cumulative 124 cases.
”伊朗卫生部3月6日宣布，自周四（5日）以来，该国新增1234例新冠肺炎病例，累计确诊4747例。
Iran's health ministry announced Thursday that 1,234 new cases of pneumonia have been diagnosed since Thursday, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 4,747.
据法新社消息，伊朗新增17例死亡病例，累计死亡124例。
According to AFP, Iran has 17 new deaths, a cumulative 124 deaths.
周五本是穆斯林聚集在清真寺进行礼拜的日子，但本周五伊朗全国范围内的礼拜活动已经全部取消，近6万处清真寺关闭。
Friday was supposed to be a day for Muslims to congregate in mosques, but Friday prayers were cancelled across Iran and nearly 60,000 mosques were closed.
伊朗外长扎里夫5日在推特上表示，伊朗正与世界卫生组织密切合作，抗击新冠肺炎疫情，保障感染者得到适当的救治。
Iran is working closely with the World Health Organization (WHO) to combat the outbreak of pneumonia and ensure that infected people receive appropriate treatment, Foreign Minister Zarif said on Tuesday.
伊方还将实施严格的防疫措施，包括在机场对入境旅客进行严密监控。
The Iraqi side will also implement strict anti-epidemic measures, including strict surveillance of inbound passengers at airports.
扎里夫还附上了一段伊朗机场配备有热成像仪的视频。
Zarif also attached a video of an Iranian airport equipped with a thermal imager.
据阿拉比亚电视台网站5日报道，伊朗传染病专家、伊朗国家流感委员会委员马尔达尼（Masoud Mardani）说，未来两周，首都德黑兰可能有多达40%的人感染新冠病毒。
As many as 40 percent of people in the capital, Tehran, are likely to be infected within the next two weeks, said Masoud Mardani, an Iranian infectious disease expert and member of Iran's National Influenza Committee.
伊朗卫生部已经宣布启用国家动员计划。
The Iranian Ministry of Health has announced the launch of a national mobilization plan.
根据计划，疑似感染者将到医疗机构接受检测，检测结果为阳性的病例将被居家隔离，并收到药物和使用说明。
According to the plan, suspected infected persons will be tested in medical institutions, and cases with positive test results will be isolated at home and given medication and instructions for use.
该计划将包括伊朗全部城市、郊区和乡村的约1.7万个卫生中心以及9000个医疗和临床中心。
The plan will include approximately 17,000 health centres and 9,000 medical and clinical centres throughout Iran's cities, suburbs and villages.
伊朗第一副总统贾汉吉里（Eshaq Jahangir）5日与德黑兰、库姆、厄尔布尔市等7个省份的官员通电话，要求要动员所有力量和设备救治病人，控制疫情传播。
Iran's First Vice President Eshaq Jahangir 5 and Tehran, Qom, Earl City, seven provinces officials to mobilize all forces and equipment to treat patients, control the spread of the epidemic.
贾汉吉里说，全社会的团结和国家的决心将帮助 伊朗尽快渡过这次危机。
Jahangiri says the unity of society and the resolve of the country will help Iran overcome the crisis as soon as possible.
伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队司令萨拉米（General Salami）5日表示，伊朗现正被卷入一场生物战争，敌人试图利用经济压力和心理行动，使伊朗人民的处境更加艰难，但伊朗从不会在战争中失败。
Iran is embroiled in a biological war and the enemy is trying to use economic pressure and psychological action to make the situation of the Iranian people more difficult, but Iran will never lose the war, said General Salami, commander of Iran's Islamic Revolutionary Guard.
伊朗的新冠肺炎疫情还扩散到中东多国，波斯湾国家已无一幸免。
Iran's outbreak of pneumonia has also spread to many countries in the Middle East, including the Persian Gulf.
